        "Calculate entropy bounds from violation",
        "Include detection efficiency impact",
        "Estimate achievable key rate",
        "Compare to trusted-device rates"
      ],
      "expectedOutput": "DI-QKD rate estimation tool",
      "hints": [
        "Key rate depends on Bell violation margin",
        "Detection efficiency is critical",
        "Rates much lower than standard QKD",
        "Trade-off: security vs rate"
      ]
    },
